Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}増していく代償
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}向かう先が地獄だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}後悔なんてない Anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Fallin' fallin' down 暗闇へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But, never going back 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狼煙高く上げて Now dive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}煩悩なんてモノ Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}性懲りも無く Fight 仲間と
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I won't run away from my sin no more
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何処までも抗って Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 超えていく 恐れずに Bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not afraid, bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.24,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if I'm drown in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:35.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分のチカラに変え Wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 捻じ曲げる System
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.32,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never ever follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:46.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 立ち向かう and I'll defeat myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:34.36,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像人性一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.28,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你将凝视深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.27,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那里有七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}当你踏入其中 你会发觉自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}踏入未知领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那些漂亮话 早就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.52,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人得以为人的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:54.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总是伴随着我们 对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}致命的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.16,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:57.11,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不要转移视线 赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.56,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只是向前 向前 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.19,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须再次取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}代价在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.00,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使前方是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.71,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不再有任何后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.64,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坠落 坠落 堕入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.19,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是 永远不回头 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.16,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}高举烽烟 然后潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.37,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与烦恼说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.99,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惩前毖后 与伙伴一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.01,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}活着就是为了择日赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再逃避我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.10,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我将一直抗争下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.69,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 无畏地超越 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.55,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不害怕 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使我将陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:35.55,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也要将其转化为我的力量 消除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.68,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 扭曲这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.11,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.32,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:46.28,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 我将面对挑战并战胜自己
